version_description: Put a capo on the first fret and this song can be played with mostly open chords.
Full chord version of tab, with strumming patterns.
Acoustic adaptation of this song in C tuning with capo on 1st fret. not at all accurate in terms of the sound, but it allows you to play it, uh, in acoustic.
Chord rendition, includes solo, interludes etc.
These are not the actual chords that can be found in the song, but they follow the melody well and sound great as part of an acoustic version. Sounds great in standard tuning as well as Eb tuning.
